The following code is used to describe SP monsters for each breed:

SP-U Breeds which must be unlocked.
SP-O "Open". Monsters who are immediately available with password.
SP-L "Legendary" Monsters which require a password and participation in a storyline event to become available.

More details on the SP varieties are found in the FAQ.
